### Backend API Test File
### Sử dụng REST Client extension trong VS Code để test
###
### Cách lấy JWT Token:
### 1. Đăng nhập vào frontend
### 2. Mở Browser DevTools > Console
### 3. Chạy: const { data } = await supabase.auth.getSession(); console.log(data.session.access_token);
### 4. Copy token và thay thế YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE bên dưới

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Get All Categories (cần JWT token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Category by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories/YOUR_CATEGORY_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Create New Category
POST http://localhost:3000/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Dự án mới",
  "description": "Mô tả dự án",
  "color": "#ff6b6b"
}

###

### Update Category
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/categories/YOUR_CATEGORY_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Tên dự án đã cập nhật",
  "description": "Mô tả mới",
  "color": "#4ecdc4"
}

###

### Delete Category
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/categories/YOUR_CATEGORY_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Categories by Group
GET http://localhost:3000/api/categories/group/YOUR_GROUP_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

